op 40\">{{cite web |title=Madison Beer Chart History\u00a0(CHR/Top 40) |url=https://www.billboard.com/music/madison-beer/chart-history/CTF |work=Billboard |accessdate=January 31, 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique|FRA]]<br><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://lescharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Madison+Beer|title=Discographie Madison Beer|website=lescharts.com|access-date=April 10, 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Irish Singles Chart|IRE]]<br><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://irish-charts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Madison+Beer|title=Discography Madison Beer|website=irish-charts.com|url-status=live|access-date=April 10, 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[VG-lista|NOR]]<br><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://norwegiancharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Madison+Beer|title=Discography Madison Beer|website=norwegiancharts.com|url-status=live|access-date=April 10, 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Official New Zealand Music Chart|NZ<br />Hot]]<br /><ref>Peaks on the NZ Hot Singles Chart:\n* \"Pop/Stars\": {{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/hotsingles?chart=4552|title=NZ Hot 40 Singles|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|date=November 12, 2018|accessdate=November 9, 2018}}\n* \"Hurts Like Hell\": {{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/hotsingles?chart=4555|title=NZ Hot Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=November 19, 2018|accessdate=November 16, 2018}}\n* \"Dear Society\": {{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/hotsingles?chart=4644|title=NZ Hot Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=May 27, 2019|accessdate=May 24, 2019}}\n* \"Good in Goodbye\": {{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/hotsingles?chart=4817|title=NZ Hot Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=February 10, 2020|accessdate=February 8, 2020}}\n* \"Selfish\" and \"Stained Glass\": {{cite web|url=h